---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Privacy Policy | Elevate Your Divine"
    description="Privacy policy for Elevate Your Divine, LLC."
>
    <div id="top">
        <header
            class="sticky top-0 z-50 overflow-visible border-b border-white/10 bg-zinc-950/60 backdrop-blur supports-[backdrop-filter]:bg-zinc-950/50"
        >
            <div
                class="mx-auto flex h-16 max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-4"
            >
                <a href="/#top" class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <img
                        src="/images/elevate.PNG"
                        alt="Elevate your Divine logo"
                        class="h-28 w-auto max-w-[220px] object-contain translate-y-2"
                        loading="eager"
                    />
                </a>

                <nav class="hidden items-center gap-3 md:flex">
                    <a
                        href="/#services"
                        class="btn-ghost inline-flex items-center justify-center"
                        >Services</a
                    >
                    <a
                        href="/#program"
                        class="btn-ghost inline-flex items-center justify-center"
                        >Program</a
                    >
                    <a
                        href="/#about"
                        class="btn-ghost inline-flex items-center justify-center"
                        >About</a
                    >
                    <a
                        href="/#contact"
                        class="btn-solid inline-flex items-center justify-center"
                        >Free Consultation</a
                    >
                </nav>
            </div>

            <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-3 md:hidden">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <a
                        href="/#services"
                        class="btn-ghost inline-flex items-center justify-center"
                        >Services</a
                    >
                    <a
                        href="/#program"
                        class="btn-ghost inline-flex items-center justify-center"
                        >Program</a
                    >
                    <a
                        href="/#about"
                        class="btn-ghost inline-flex items-center justify-center"
                        >About</a
                    >
                    <a
                        href="/#contact"
                        class="btn-solid inline-flex items-center justify-center"
                        >Free Consultation</a
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>
    </div>

    <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16">
        <article class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">
                Privacy Policy
            </h1>

            <br />
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200">
                Last Updated: February 6, 2026
            </p>

            <br />

            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200">
                We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your
                personal information.
            </p>

            <br />

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">
                Information We Collect
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200">We may collect:</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-zinc-200">
                <li>Name, email, phone number</li>
                <li>Billing and payment information</li>
                <li>Booking and appointment details</li>
                <li>Documents required for notary services</li>
                <li>Communications sent to us</li>
            </ul>

            <br />
            <br />

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">
                How We Use Information
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200">
                Your information is used to:
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-zinc-200">
                <li>Provide services</li>
                <li>Process payments</li>
                <li>Schedule appointments</li>
                <li>Communicate with you</li>
                <li>Meet legal and regulatory obligations</li>
            </ul>

            <br />
            <br />

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">
                Notary-Specific Privacy
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200">
                Notary records are maintained as required by Texas law and may
                be disclosed if legally required.
            </p>

            <br />
            <br />

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">
                Sharing Information
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200">
                We do not sell your personal data. Information may be shared
                with:
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-zinc-200">
                <li>Payment processors</li>
                <li>Scheduling platforms</li>
                <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>
            </ul>

            <br />
            <br />

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">
                Data Security
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200">
                We take reasonable steps to protect your data but cannot
                guarantee absolute security of online transmissions.
            </p>

            <br />
            <br />

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">
                Your Rights
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200">
                You may request access, correction, or deletion of your personal
                information, subject to legal retention requirements.
            </p>

            <br />
        </article>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
